Helen Jerome Eddy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helen_Jerome_Eddy 0 Helen Jerome Eddy (February 25, 1897 – January 27, 1990) was a motion picture actress from New York, New York. She was noted as a character actress who played genteel heroines in films such as Rebecca of Sunnybrook Farm (1917).
